data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath split level home located in a cul-de-sac on over half an acre. This home features a large recreation room in the basement, bonus room that is currently being used as a playroom, fenced in backyard and two working, wood burning fireplaces. New roof, gutters & downspouts (November 2022); Kitchen remodel completed (September 2022); New flooring on main level (April 2023).  The Forest Ridge neighborhood includes multiple pools, tennis courts, basketball courts and many community events throughout the year. It's also located near multiple metro parks, a recreation complex, Eastwood lake, museums and WPAFB.   There are many opportunities for you to bring your own ideas to personalize this home and make it your own!
